<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f0f9ff; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 32px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #dde8f5; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706); padding: 32px 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; }
    .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .body { padding: 32px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 16px; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .card { background: #fff7ed; border: 1px solid #fed7aa; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .card-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .card-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .label { font-size: 12px; color: #92400e; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; min-width: 100px; padding-top: 2px; }
    .value { font-size: 14px; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 500; }
    .highlight { background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: #92400e; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; }
    .footer { background: #fffbeb; padding: 20px 32px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #fed7aa; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>⏰ Recordatorio de cita</h1>
      <p>Tu cita es mañana</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p class="greeting">Hola, <strong>{{ patientName }}</strong> </p>
      <div class="highlight">
        🗓️ Tienes una cita médica <strong>mañana {{ date }} a las {{ time }}</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-row">
          <span class="label">Médico</span>
          <span class="value">Dr. {{ doctorName }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-row">
          <span class="label">Especialidad</span>
          <span class="value">{{ specialty }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-row">
          <span class="label">Fecha</span>
          <span class="value">{{ date }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-row">
          <span class="label">Hora</span>
          <span class="value">{{ time }}</span>
        </div>
        {% if reason %}
        <div class="card-row">
          <span class="label">Motivo</span>
          <span class="value">{{ reason }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <p style="color:#64748b;font-size:13px;">Por favor, acude con antelación. Si necesitas cancelar, hazlo desde la aplicación.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Salute — Sistema de gestión médica</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
